  "title": "Cost Accountant (Manufacturing)",
  "description": "<p><em>A well-established company in the </em><em><strong>manufacturing sector</strong></em><em> is looking for an experienced Cost Accountant to </em><em><strong>oversee costing, budgeting, and financial reporting activities.</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle month-end closing and execute product costing runs using SAP.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate budget planning and liaise with various departments.</li>\n  <li>Monitor manufacturing costs and manage inventory for finished goods, spare parts, consumables, and WIP.</li>\n  <li>Prepare cost control reports, perform financial analysis, and assist in management reporting.</li>\n  <li>Support ad-hoc finance projects and internal audits.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Accountancy or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 4 years’ experience in<strong> costing</strong> within a <strong>manufacturing environment.</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>SAP</strong> with strong Excel and PowerPoint skills.</li>\n  <li>Excellent analytical, communication, and interpersonal abilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
